Collect resource names from a data frame

Source: R/resources.R
resources_in.Rd

Collect resource names from a data frame

Usage

resources_in(data)

Arguments

data

A data frame from an OmniPath query.

Value

Character: resource names occuring in the data frame.

Examples

pathways <- omnipath_interactions()
resources_in(pathways)
